_sText:
My first minigame map based to moomin.
This is v2_1 so its only have 6 mini-games

Games:
Groke:
-try to survive for groke attack
Airship:
- Kill other players with knife and low gravity
Ufo:
- Ufo is in moominvalley and its want to kill everyone
Race:
- Run to the finish to win
Desert-Battle:
- Kill other players with scout and smokegrenades
Fish
- You are in the lake where is big fish

Notes:

+ Good music
+ All associated with "moomin"
+ Muligame map 
- it could be more beatiful
- and other stuff

Sound of Groke is finnish groke sound because its the best.

I hope good gameplay moments to all.
Comment please!
